<p>
  Devise is a flexible authentication solution for Rails based on Warden. This guide outlines how to set up and configure Devise with its available feature options,
  including <code>Authenticatable</code>, <code>Confirmable</code>, <code>DatabaseAuthenticatable</code>, <code>Lockable</code>, <code>Recoverable</code>, <code>Registerable</code>, <code>Rememberable</code>, <code>Timeoutable</code>, <code>Trackable</code>,
  and <code>Validatable</code>.
</p>

<div class='alert alert-secondary'>
  <h5>Add the Devise Gem</h5>
  <p>
    Follow the official Devise documentation for installation instructions:<br />
